OL,3,CResident doctors in England to be
OL,4,Cballoted on strike action, BMA says
OL,6,FResident doctors in England will
OL,7,Fballot for strike action over pay, the
OL,8,FBritish Medical Association (BMA) has
OL,9,Fannounced.
OL,11,FThe union said three weeks had passed
OL,12,Fsince it warned the government of the
OL,13,F"consequences of the absence of a
OL,14,Freasonable, timely pay offer".
OL,16,FThe ballot will open on May 27 and
OL,17,Fclose on July 7.
