OL,3,CResident doctors in England to be
OL,4,Cballoted on strike action, BMA says
OL,6,FResident doctor is the new term for
OL,7,Fjunior doctor and refers to more than
OL,8,F50,000 qualified doctors working in GP
OL,9,Fpractices and hospitals, from
OL,10,Fgraduates to medics with a decade of
OL,11,Fexperience.
OL,13,FCo-chairs of BMA's resident doctors'
OL,14,Fcommittee, Dr Melissa Ryan and Dr Ross
OL,15,FNieuwoudt, said: "Today we met with
OL,16,FWes Streeting and made clear that all
OL,17,Fhe would have to do to avoid the need
OL,18,Ffor a ballot was pledge to negotiate a
OL,19,Ffair deal that moved us toward pay
OL,20,Frestoration by 2027, in line with
OL,21,Fexisting BMA policy.
