OL,3,CResident doctors in England to be
OL,4,Cballoted on strike action, BMA says
OL,6,F"Unfortunately, he could not make this
OL,7,Fcommitment.
OL,9,F"Resident doctors are not going to be
OL,10,Fignored. We are going to stand up for
OL,11,Four value to the NHS and to patients,
OL,12,Fand we are going to fight to stay on
OL,13,Fthe path set out for us by last year's
OL,14,Fdeal: restoration of our pay to the
OL,15,Flevel of 2008.
OL,17,F"No doctor today is worth less than
OL,18,Fthey were 17 years ago, and that is
OL,19,Fprecisely what doctors voting 'yes' to
OL,20,Findustrial action will be telling the
OL,21,Fgovernment.
