OL,3,CResident doctors in England to be
OL,4,Cballoted on strike action, BMA says
OL,6,F"We don't want to be in the situation
OL,7,Fwhere we have to fight over and over
OL,8,Fagain for our worth ` we would rather
OL,9,Fget on with our careers and our work
OL,10,Fcaring for our patients."
OL,12,FSince 2011, resident doctor members of
OL,13,Fthe BMA have taken industrial action
OL,14,F11 times.
OL,16,FNHS England estimates the walkouts led
OL,17,Fto almost 1.5 million appointments
OL,18,Fbeing cancelled or rescheduled.
