OL,3,CResident doctors in England to be
OL,4,Cballoted on strike action, BMA says
OL,6,FThe last strike took place on June 27
OL,7,Fto July 2, just days before the
OL,8,Fgeneral election.
OL,10,FIn September, BMA members voted to
OL,11,Faccept a Government pay deal worth
OL,12,F22.3% on average over two years.
OL,14,FThe deal included a pay rise of
OL,15,Fbetween 3.71% and 5.05% ` averaging
OL,16,F4.05% ` for resident doctors, on top
OL,17,Fof an existing pay award for 2023/24,
OL,18,Fwhich was backdated to April 2023.
