OL,6,FEach part of the pay scale was
OL,7,Fuplifted by 6%, plus #1,000, as
OL,8,Frecommended by the Review Body on
OL,9,FDoctors' and Dentists' Remuneration
OL,10,F(DDRB), with an effective date of
OL,11,FApril 1 2024.
OL,13,FThe government also committed to work
OL,14,Fwith the BMA to streamline how
OL,15,Fresident doctors report any additional
OL,16,Fhours they work, along with reforms to
OL,17,Ftraining.
